org.telesocial.rest.api
Interface TelesocialClient

All Known Implementing Classes:
TelesocialClientImpl
public interface TelesocialClient

TelesocialClient represents an interface to Telesocial for a particular application. Each TelesocialClient instance is associated with a particular TelesocialApplication The client exposes methods for creating and manipulating different resources on Telesocial server Instances of TelesocialClient can be created with Telesocial.createClient(String, String) factory method

Author:
Shamaila Tahir
See Also:
Telesocial.createClient(String, String)
